  <summary>9/16/1987--Introduced.
Declares that the National Rural Crisis Response Center is deserving of recognition, encouragement, and support of the Congress and the American people. Recognizes the Center for the valuable service being rendered and authorizes and requests the President to issue a proclamation calling on the people to recognize, encourage, and support the Center.</summary>
